pageProduct.name: Voost Energy Effervescent 60 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

VÖOST Energy - Daily Multivitamin + Guarana

VÖOST the great tasting vitamin BOOST

We're passionate about all things effervescent and we're on a mission to make vitamin supplements a bit more appealing! We're armed with the world's largest range of effervescent vitamins and minerals to help you find just the right one to suit your needs.

Simple to use. Premium formulation. Great tasting.

Effervescent Vitamins and Minerals

Suitable For: Vegan Friendly

Size: 60 Tablets

Flavour: Orange & Mango

Serving Size: 1 Tablet

Servings Per Pack: 60

KEY FEATURES

• VÖOST Energy Helps Support Energy Production
• VÖOST Energy Helps Support Energy Production
• VÖOST Energy Helps Support Energy Production
• VÖOST Energy Helps Support Energy Production

Warnings

ALWAYS READ THE LABEL. FOLLOW THE DIRECTIONS FOR USE.
Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Adults only. Keep out of reach of children. Contains caffeine (74 mg per tablet) Total caffeine (80 mg per tablet). A cup of instant coffee contains approximately 80 mg of caffeine. Caffeine intake more than 200 mg per day is not recommended during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Store tube tightly closed in a cool, dry place. Store below 25°C. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing.

Ingredients

Thiamine (B1) (as Thiamine Mononitrate) 1.1 mg
Riboflavine (B2) (Riboflavin Sodium Phosphate) 1.4 mg
Nicotinamide 16 mg
Pantothenic Acid (B5) (as Calcium Pantothenate) 6 mg
Pyridoxine (B6) (as Pyridoxine Hydrochloride) 1.4 mg
Cyanocobalamin (B12) 2.5 microgram
Folic Acid 200 microgram
Biotin 50 microgram
Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C) 80 mg
DL-Alpha-Tocopherol (Vitamin E) (as DL-Alpha-Tocopheryl Acetate) 12 mg
Calcium (as Calcium Carbonate) 100 mg
Magnesium (as Magnesium Carbonate Hydrate) 100 mg
Zinc (as Zinc Sulfate Monohydrate) 10 mg
Caffeine 74 mg
Paullinia Cupana (Guarana) Extract 60 mg equiv. dry seed 195 mg (Equiv Caffeine 6 mg)
Total Caffeine all sources 80 mg
Each tablet contains 170 mg of sodium
Contains Sucralose

Contains: Each tablet contains 170 mg of sodium
Contains Sucralose

Directions

Adults: Take 1 tablet daily, dissolved in 200 ml of water, or as directed by your health professional.

USAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Start with 200mL of fresh water.
Add one Voost tablet & watch it fizz.
Once dissolved, it's ready to drink!
Experience the fizz!

Adults: Take 1 tablet daily, dissolved in 200mL of water, or as directed by your healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store tube tightly closed in a cool, dry place. Store below 25°C. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing.

Storage Temperature: Below 25°C.

RECYCLABLE INFORMATION

Please recycle this box.

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
